<h3>PALS (Patient advice and liaison service)</h3>
<p><a href="mailto:cdda-tr.patientexperiencecddft@nhs.net">cdda-tr.patientexperiencecddft@nhs.net</a></p>
<div class="pals-text">
<p>You can talk to PALS who provide confidential advice and support to patients, families and their carers, and can provide information on the NHS and health related matters.</p>
<p>Patients should  contact the Patient Experience Team on 0800 7835774 or via e-mail patient.experience@cddft.nhs.uk</p>
